45
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:09,760
[Lianhe Town Government]

46
00:02:09,760 --> 00:02:13,040
Next,
let's have Mr. Dou give his speech.

47
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:25,360
Thank you all for coming here.

48
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,840
I am very honored

49
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:30,600
