and admired by the whole town.

50
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,040
It's my honor.

51
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:36,000
From now on, I will do everything I can

52
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:38,440
to lead the folks of Lianhe Town

53
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,400
to live better lives

54
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:44,640
and create a more peaceful home
for everyone.

55
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,240
Yes!

56
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:54,960
I hereby declare the ribbon-cutting
ceremony for the county annals starts now.

57
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:59,240
I invite my daughter, Dou Lili,
to come cut the ribbon with me.

58
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:01,440
Detective Wang, come here too.

59
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,560
Are you ready?

60
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:16,240
One, two, three.

61
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,840
What?

62
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,720
Isn't this an opium shipping contract?

63
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:28,840
This is so shameless.

64
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,630
How can he do this?

65
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:35,780
- Hear, hear!
- Yes!

66
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,320
They are indeed shipping opium!

67
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,000
How shameless.

68
00:03:39,180 --> 00:03:40,420
[The mayor's secret deals]
Shameless!

69
00:03:41,580 --> 00:03:42,460
[Mayor's daughter
hooking up with reporters]

70
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,680
[Evidence of drug dealing]
What an animal!

71
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,120
He doesn't deserve to be the mayor!

72
00:03:50,980 --> 00:03:52,460
[The mayor's absurd private life]

73
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:58,990
How could he do this?

74
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:02,520
So she really hooked up with reporters!

75
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:05,480
Last time, we got nothing
because this woman sacrificed herself

76
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,960
to bribe journalists.

77
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:10,560
It is because of you
that Lianhe Town has become a foul town.

78
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,000
Step down, Dou Huaizhong!

79
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,640
Dou Huaizhong, you animal!

80
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:15,560
Detective Wang,
get rid of the troublemakers!

81
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,300
What are you doing?

82
00:04:16,300 --> 00:04:17,090
Go away!

83
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:45,680
These are all a misunderstanding.

84
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,880
Please calm down, everyone.

85
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,560
Please let me explain.

86
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,920
Please calm down.

87
00:04:57,050 --> 00:04:58,920
- Bastard!
- We'll kill you, jerk!

88
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,640
Dou Huaizhong, step down!

89
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,480
[A week ago]
(So, you mean,)

90
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,340
(we will write county annals)

91
00:05:07,340 --> 00:05:09,040
[Mayor's Office]
(for the people-loving Mayor)

92
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:12,120
(to comprehensively record)

93
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,720
(his great achievements,)

94
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:15,320
(and then...)

95
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,960
Make it public.

96
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,080
(In the meantime,)

97
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,200
(I will collect Dou Huaizhong's
opium trading accounts)

98
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:25,360
(based on available information,)

99
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,920
