102
00:05:32,860 --> 00:05:34,980
[Account Bill]

103
00:05:36,570 --> 00:05:38,640
Corrupted jerk!
You don't deserve to be the mayor!

104
00:05:39,130 --> 00:05:40,770
Boo! Step down!

105
00:05:43,650 --> 00:05:45,170
Beat him!

106
00:05:45,170 --> 00:05:46,420
- Step down!
- Bastard!

107
00:05:46,420 --> 00:05:47,810
Step down!

108
00:05:47,810 --> 00:05:48,660
Resign!

109
00:05:49,330 --> 00:05:50,810
You're not our mayor!

110
00:05:50,810 --> 00:05:52,920
- How could you do something like this?
- Shameless!

111
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:56,500
- Jerk!
- How dare you!

112
00:05:56,500 --> 00:05:57,420
Step down!

113
