I'm sorry, Guanwen.

114
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,640
I didn't want you to get hurt.

115
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,080
If you disappear again
without telling me,

116
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,920
I won't forgive you anymore.

117
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:21,920
OK.

118
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,800
